quran[9{c,v,t}:
3,1,alif laam mem
3,2,"Allah , woh zindah Javed hasti, jo nizaam kaayenaat ko sambhale hue hai, haqeeqat mein uss ke siwa koi khuda nahi hai"
3,3,"uss ne tum par yeh kitaab nazil ki hai, jo haq le kar aayi hai aur unn kitabon ki tasdeeq kar rahi hai jo pehlay se aayi hui theen is se pehlay woh insanon ki hadaayat ke liye torat aur injeel nazil kar chuka hai"
3,4,"aur is ne woh kasoti utari hai ( jo haq aur baatil ka farq daal khanay wali hai ) ab jo log Allah ke Faramin ko qubool karne se inkaar karen, un ko yaqeenan sakht saza miley gi Allah be panah taaqat ka maalik hai aur buraiee ka badla dainay wala hai"
3,5,zameen aur aasman ki koi cheez Allah se posheeda nahi
3,6,"wohi to hai jo tumhari maaon ke pait mein tumhari soorten, jaisi chahta hai, banata hai uss zabardast hikmat walay ke siwa koi aur khuda nahi hai"
3,7,"wohi khuda hai, jis ne yeh kitaab tum par nazil ki hai iss kitaab mein do terhan ki ayaat hain : aik mohkmaat , jo kitaab ki asal bunyaad hain aur doosri mutashbihaat , jin logon ke dalo n mein theerh hai, woh ftne ki talaash mein hameshamutashabihaathi ke peechay parre rehtay hain aur unn ko maienay pehnanay ki koshish kya karte hain, halaank un ka haqeeqi mafhuum Allah ke siwa koi nahi jaanta ,bakhaf iss ke jo log ilm mein pukhta car hain, woh kehte hain ke"" hamara unn par imaan hai, yeh sab hamaray Rab hi ki taraf se hain"" aur sach yeh hai ke kisi cheez se sahih sabaq sirf danishmand log hi haasil karte hain"
3,8,"woh Allah se dua karte rehtay hain ke :"" parvar-digaar! jab to hamein seedhay rasta par laga chuka hai, to phir kahin hamaray dilon ko kajji mein mubtala nah kar dejyu hamein apne khazana Faiz se rehmat ataa kar ke to hi Fayaz haqeeqi hai"
3,9,"parvar-digaar! to yaqeenan sab logon ko aik roz jama karne wala hai, jis ke anay mein koi shuba nahi to hargiz apne waday se talnay wala nahi hai """
